{"tid":2334631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"42 歲藍屍李秋芝認公眾地方打鬥罪判 160 小時社服令","createTime":"2020-12-21T09:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T10:40:03.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f753264a9447ebde780155a9b985096b4b71d3d","tid":2334631,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"「元朗721事件」七個月，示威者於銅鑼灣時代廣場發起「和你 lunch」行動，其間有愛國人士「踩場」，雙方爆及肢體衝突，當中被稱為「正義姐」的教師藍雪寶疑遭數名人士「私了」，最終兩男兩女被捕，案中屬<span class=\"red\">親中陣營、內地移居香港的婦人</span>，早前承認在公眾地方打鬥罪，今（21日）被判 160 小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n現年 42 歲、<span class=\"red\">操普通話的售貨員李秋芝</span>早前向感化官表示，她是因「自衞」犯案，其律師在庭上澄清，李一度錯誤理解「自衞」一詞之意，經法律代表解釋後，承認自己在關鍵時間犯案並非出於「自衞」，故要求法庭將相關字句刪去。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官錢禮批准上述修訂，並稱李最大的求情理由在於及時認罪，遂判共 160 小時社會服務令，且需支付 500 元訟費。"},{"pid":"dbcab1c79cb15772f451759cbc668c8dc0a76785","tid":2334631,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%81%95-%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E5%A7%90-%E8%B8%A9%E5%A0%B4%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0-lunch-%E8%AE%8A%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5-42-%E6%AD%B2%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E5%A9%A6%E5%88%A4-160-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2581%2595-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AC%25A5-42-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E5%2588%25A4-160-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=4fe90e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2581%2595-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25A7%2590-%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0-lunch-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25AC%25A5-42-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E6